event.description:
Founder Mode 2025 is a two-night retreat in Healdsburg for our closest friends of YC and alums. PG, Jessica, and the full YC partnership will be in attendance, along with some remarkable guest speakers.

Instructions:
We are excited to welcome you to the Founder Mode Retreat 2025!

The core of the program will take place at Montage Healdsburg . Hotel rooms are divided across Montage and Hotel Healdsburg (a lovely hotel downtown - walking distance to the off-site activities). Hotel assignments will be released the week of August 4 - please keep an eye out via email for your specific details.

We have confirmed your attendance for Aug.13 - 15, and we ask that you plan to attend all events starting 6 PM Wednesday, through Friday morning. Please review the schedule and email [retreat@ycombinator.com](mailto:retreat@ycombinator.com) if the below pertains to you:

* If you are no longer able to attend part of the retreat
* If you have any dietary restrictions or allergies
* If you plan to coordinate your own transportation to & from the retreat

event.description:
Founder Mode 2025 is a two-night retreat in Healdsburg for our closest friends of YC and alums. PG, Jessica, and the full YC partnership will be in attendance, along with some remarkable guest speakers.

Instructions:
We are excited to welcome you to the Founder Mode Retreat 2025!

The core of the program will take place at Montage Healdsburg . Hotel rooms are divided across Montage and Hotel Healdsburg (a lovely hotel downtown - walking distance to the off-site activities). Hotel assignments will be released the week of August 4 - please keep an eye out via email for your specific details.

We have confirmed your attendance for Aug.13 - 15, and we ask that you plan to attend all events starting 6 PM Wednesday, through Friday morning. Please review the schedule and email [retreat@ycombinator.com](mailto:retreat@ycombinator.com) if the below pertains to you:

* If you are no longer able to attend part of the retreat
* If you have any dietary restrictions or allergies
* If you plan to coordinate your own transportation to & from the retreat
